&lt;li&gt;Proven record with client-facing project management or owners&#39; rep experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong interpersonal skills, and written, and verbal communication.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must have strong client facing skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to troubleshoot software for client.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge and experience in value engineering, scope development, and project delivery methods in the public sector are preferred; JOC (Job Order Contracting) experience and understanding is a huge plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-motivated and able to work well independently in a strict deadline-oriented environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong skills in Microsoft Office Suite and the ability to quickly adapt to additional software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
