&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;This is an excellent opportunity for someone who gets restless sitting behind a desk and likes to travel! Candidates who do well in this role often have a background as a Journeyman or Master Electrician, Maintenance Electrician, and/or Instrumentational and Electrical Technician for an institutional employer. Projects are typically short and range from one to six months. Field deployments are typically one week in length and usually not more than two per month.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
